The second mistake was not forcing Valdez to leave the country for his own safety after seizing other papers that had printed the same story.
Valdez has become a legend in Mexico and abroad, and his death is seen as an important milestone in the fight by Mexican criminals against journalists.
He'd managed to survive for so long, and all his friends and colleagues believed that would never change.
